          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">普通攻擊</span></p><p>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_3053715211823282497.png",
                "id": "talent54383",
                "key": "拯救之焰",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "拯救之焰"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素戰技</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/5472faa96cc230f0c6a742c278748e91_1578929642218871064.png",
                "id": "talent1426",
                "key": "熾烈箴言",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "熾烈箴言"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆發</span></p><p>造成3點<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素傷害</span>，召喚<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">黯火爐心</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/1cfb4a644ede1096bcf61f228e14be0a_601213028830479838.png",
                "id": "talent10367",
                "key": "天隕預兆",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "pyro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "天隕預兆"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">被動技能</span></p><p>【被動】戰鬥開始時，初始附屬<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">火之新生</span>。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">火之新生</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">狀態</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">所附屬角色被擊倒時：</span>移除此效果，使角色<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">免於被擊倒</span>，並治療該角色到3點生命值。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/21/7998136/241466b9ccdefb6219ef6bf74cd493e2_4240055551771842897.png",
                "id": "talent39412",
                "key": "火之新生",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火之新生"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">結束階段：</span>造成1點<span style=\"color: #FF9999\">火元素傷害</span>，對所有敵方後臺角色造成1點<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6469041152836152952.png",
                "key": "黯火爐心",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/2cce1877020bad6ed9476a8bb8db436c_903215387760480184.png",
                "title": "黯火爐心"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附著火元素，可發生元素反應：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">融化</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">蒸發</span>：本傷害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">超載</span>：本傷害+2，目標強制切換到下一個角色</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">燃燒</span>：本傷害+1，生成回合結束時造成1點火元素傷害的<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">[燃燒烈焰]</span>（可用次數1，最多疊加到2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/d714b3b669cc08d1d8e34464fd7a3630_7825029569487209683.png",
                "key": "火元素傷害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "火元素傷害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透傷害</span></strong></p><p>穿透傷害無法受到傷害加成，但是也無法被護盾、傷害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果觸發後，會消耗1次<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次數</span>耗盡後，立刻棄置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">免於被擊倒</span></strong></p><p>一些效果會使角色在生命值被降為0的時候<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">免於被擊倒</span>，並治療該角色到一定生命值。</p><p>此時，角色不視為被<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">擊倒</span>過。（因此，角色所附屬的裝備和狀態不會被棄置，充能也不會被清空。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/05/25/7998136/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_562991060341062189.png",
                "key": "規則解釋",
